essings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever performs twelve cycles of prayer in each day and night, a house will be built for them in Paradise.\" Umm Habibah said, \"I have never abandoned them since I heard it from the Messenger of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12935,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/18\/sunan-prayers-dhuhur-fajr\/","url_meta":{"origin":33674,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Sunan of Dhuhur and Fajr prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would never miss four cycles before noon prayer and two cycles before dawn prayer. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1182 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u062f\u064e\u0639\u064f \u0623\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0639\u064b\u0627 \u0642\u064e\u0628\u0652\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28132,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/nawafil-witr-sunan-fajr\/","url_meta":{"origin":33674,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Praying Witr prayer, Sunan of dawn prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would pray at night, two by two, and make it odd with one cycle. The Prophet would pray two cycles before the morning prayer, so lightly as if the call to prayer were in his ears. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14755,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/28\/salat-al-fajr-khayr-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":33674,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Sunan prayer of Fajr better than world","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTwo cycles of prayer\u00a0before the dawn\u00a0prayer are better than the world and everything in it. They are both more beloved to me than the entire world.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 725 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"